game.name: Wheelie Challenge 2
game.description:
You do not need to leave your home to enjoy your favorite bicycle riding activity when the internet is full of easily-controllable and graphically-improved bicycle games for boys. Yes, playing them is not as challenging as you thought of. Join Wheelie Challenge 2 to seek for extra fun and practice your racing abilities in a friendly environment! Make sure to grab as many coins as you can to purchase new bicycles and unlock new levels. Let us see how far you will be able to go while enjoying a wheelie!

Your objective in this brand new racing game is to keep your bike on one wheel for as long as you can. Pay attention to the details and achieve some challenging missions to climb the ranks in this cool html5 driving game! Make sure to pull your front wheel off the ground while maintaining your balance. When you are on your vehicle, try to wheel your bike up and down the ramps without allowing it to be toppled backwards. Operate your bike continuously not to let the front tire come back down!

Make your stickman begin the bike riding fun by just clicking and holding on the screen in this highly-addictive bike game! There are multiple obstacles like ramps that will be enough to make your game harder. Practice hard and try to keep your wheel in the air always to stay in the game for long! Grab the coins you see on your way to unlock new exciting bikes and add new locations to try out in this challenging driving game! Check out our wider bike racing game collection to find more maximum fun!
